You should stay in Jiangcheng for now.

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:38.760
The police still need your cooperation with the investigation.

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:39.520
Okay.

00:01:02.480 --> 00:01:03.280
Yang Xiaomei.

00:01:06.240 --> 00:01:08.000
The results of your psychiatric evaluation

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.240
and polygraph test are out.

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:12.440
Are you

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:14.700
still planning to keep up the act?

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:23.480
Yang Xiaomei,

00:01:24.080 --> 00:01:24.940
from Nancheng.

00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:27.400
You worked at the Nancheng Meat Processing Plant

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.660
and a garment factory.

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:30.880
Your dismemberment skills,

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:33.960
